0.1.8   2022-02-18

    [RETIREMENT]
    * git.io have retired their shortening service. So this module will no
      longer function. Please use a different shotener.

0.1.7   2016-01-19

    [ BUG FIX ]
    * Added LWP::Protocol::https as a prereq. It's technically only a plugin,
      which I didn't realise, so some testers are failing it due to not having
      https support.

